schools.name: Susan Miller Dorsey Senior High School

data.description: Nice little house for sale in the beautiful  city of Los Angeles, located in the epicenter of everything Los Angeles has to offer, Including downtown LA, University of California, and Hollywood, This home is centrally located to Culver city, and Santa Monica.   The home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bath it has a front and spacious back yard with a long driveway offering additional parking spaces. The home has a remodeled kitchen with granite counters, and laminated wood floors.  also it was just painted to hand over a  ready to move in home.   laundry space is in the backyard. There is a casita or mother in law quarters attached to the house with a kitchenette and two additional bedrooms, and another bathroom. currently used as storage.   Must come and see this home perfect for a larger family or two separate families come and make it your home.
